{"tid":1862914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年2月5日 — 早晨，Twitter戰線須要大家","createTime":"2020-02-05T01:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T15:28:48.000Z","uid":253983,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"35bd178031a87ef1e0fcd422c8cf62776824bbdb","tid":1862914,"uid":253983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:32:07.000Z","msg":"咁多位唔好意思呀，小弟過年開始懶左，一直無喺度出post推Twitter戰線，今日開始會努力返架喇！<br />\n<br />\n手足無放棄過我地，我地都唔可以放棄呀！<br />\n一齊完成Twitter戰線嘅任務呀！<br />\n<br />\n呢度有個今日任務嘅匯集，大家可以㩒呢條link入今日嘅任務<br />\n記得 Like + Retweet <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原Tweet</span></span> 呀 <br />\n(總係有朋友仔Like + Tweet我地個comment就算，係要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">㩒入去原Tweet先Like + Retweet</span></span>呀)<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tweetingforhk/status/1224863861133713410?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftweetingforhk%2Fstatus%2F1224863861133713410%3Fs%3D21&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3WHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=4cdb3852\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftweetingforhk%2Fstatus%2F1224863861133713410%3Fs%3D21&h=0b3144cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tweetingforhk/status/1224863861133713410?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n另外歡迎大家follow呢個Twitter，留意每日Twitter戰線任務<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTweetingforHK&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3WHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=3c19ed15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK</a>"},{"pid":"6916be622e21f5d92bb61d87e3b8c7df18cdefd9","tid":1862914,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:33:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"041e7510b3b4225f9d72a8148742aef74436462a","tid":1862914,"uid":111884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:33:55.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"68cfe8c43b975a